data.description: New Price! Welcome to your dream home in the Autumn Woods subdivision of Prairieville! This exquisite residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, spread gracefully across 2,350 square feet of living space. As you arrive, the ample parking space and convenient garage provide both comfort and convenience for you and your guests. Throughout the home, a captivating medley of ceramic tiles, plush carpets, and resilient hard flooring creates a dynamic tapestry of textures and styles. The split floorplan ensures privacy and functionality, with the primary bedroom on the first floor and the three additional bedrooms on the second floor. The vaulted ceilings in the living room create an expansive atmosphere, flooded with natural light that complements the inviting ambiance. Discover a versatile bonus room on the first floor, perfect for either an efficient office space or a tranquil sunroom retreat. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a culinary enthusiast's delight. Equipped with stainless steel appliances and adorned with sleek granite countertops, it seamlessly marries style and functionality. Indulge in delectable meals either within the cozy eat-in kitchen or the refined ambiance of the formal dining room. Retreat to the lavish primary suite that features an en suite bathroom, complete with a separate shower and a luxurious jacuzzi tub. This spa-like oasis offers the perfect escape for allowing yourself to unwind and rejuvenate in style. Stepping outside, you'll find a generously sized backyard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor recreation and entertainment. The concrete slab provides a perfect spot for an uncovered BBQ pit, where you can host gatherings and enjoy al fresco dining in the pleasant Prairieville weather. Don't miss the chance to make this incredible property your forever home. With its perfect blend of modern amenities, thoughtful design, and a prime location in the Autumn Woods subdivision, this residence encapsulates Ascension living.
